data.description:
THIS GEM IS BACK ON THE MARKET!!  BUYER'S FINANCING FELL THROUGH!

Calling all Investors and Snowbirds: This adorable 2/1 home meets all your needs. Whether you are looking for a profitable vacation rental or to escape the winter chill and embrace the sunshine lifestyle, this may be your new home. Located in Sylvan Shores, this home offers a spacious backyard with a storage shed and a white vinyl fence for privacy. A relaxing back porch that leads out to the well-kept pool that is heated with a paid off solar heating system and a newer hot water heater contribute to energy efficiency. Inside, the home features a laundry room in the garage, central air for year-round comfort and a kitchen is ready for your personal touch and upgrading. 

Conveniently located, this home is just 5.5 hours from the Keys, 2.5 hours from Miami, and 2 hours from Orlando. With the ocean only 1 hour and 30 minutes in either direction and numerous lakes nearby, including Lake Clay just blocks away. Plus, enjoy the thrill of being just 15 minutes from the Sebring International Speedway! Book a tour to see this gem before it's too late
